1. List all workspaces 
terraform workspace list


“This shows all available workspaces, with an asterisk next to the one currently active.”

 2. Create a new workspace 
terraform workspace new dev


“This creates a new workspace called dev and switches you to it.”

 3. Switch between workspaces 
terraform workspace select prod


“Use this to switch to another workspace — like moving from dev to prod.”

 4. Show current workspace
terraform workspace show


“This command displays which workspace you’re currently using.”